{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867653402,"sessionID":"ses_2860b0702ffe9Wcb8nmOnayaDo","part":{"id":"prt_d79f57227001YAi1NmRPHxeihL","messageID":"msg_d79f556c30017ftlgoawhacuVI","sessionID":"ses_2860b0702ffe9Wcb8nmOnayaDo","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_e8a39c5951fd4cfe8fc4f470","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端\n\n**Module:** sdk-python\n**Language:** Python\n**Size:** M\n\n## Purpose\n\nProvide the foundational HTTP client infrastructure for the AgentCube Python SDK, including session management with connection pooling, control plane client for Workload Manager interactions, and data plane client for Code Interpreter Router operations. This layer underpins all higher-level SDK clients (`CodeInterpreterClient`, `AgentRuntimeClient`) with consistent timeout defaults, authentication handling, and session header management.\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n- `create_session()` utility: `requests.Session` factory with `HTTPAdapter` for `http://` and `https://`, configurable `pool_connections` and `pool_maxsize`\n- `ControlPlaneClient`: HTTP client for Workload Manager control plane (`POST /v1/code-interpreter`, `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{id}`), auth token resolution from argument or Kubernetes SA token file\n- `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient`: HTTP client for Code Interpreter data plane via Router (`api/execute`, `api/files` for write/upload/download/list), session header `x-agentcube-session-id`, base URL resolution from `router_url` + namespace + CR name\n- Timeout defaults: read `120s`, connect `5.0s`, with per-call override support\n- Exception hierarchy: `AgentCubeError`, `CommandExecutionError`, `SessionError`, `DataPlaneError`\n- Utility functions: `read_token_from_file`, `get_logger`\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- `CodeInterpreterClient` high-level lifecycle (AR-027)\n- `AgentRuntimeClient` / `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` (AR-028)\n- CLI tooling, deployment, sandbox orchestration\n- E2E test infrastructure\n\n## Architecture Summary\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                  Public Client Layer                        │\n│        CodeInterpreterClient  │  AgentRuntimeClient         │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│              Data Plane Clients                             │\n│  CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient  │  AgentRuntimeDataPlane   │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│              Control Plane Client                           │\n│                   ControlPlaneClient                        │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                  HTTP Utilities                             │\n│  create_session  │  read_token_from_file  │  get_logger     │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Control Plane HTTP:**\n| Method | Path | Notes |\n|--------|------|-------|\n| `POST` | `{base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` | JSON body: `name`, `namespace`, `ttl`, `metadata`; returns `sessionId` |\n| `DELETE` | `{base_url}/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}` | 404 treated as success |\n\n**Data Plane HTTP (Code Interpreter, relative to `base_url`):**\n| Method | Path | Body |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `POST` | `api/execute` | JSON `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"<n>s\"}` |\n| `POST` | `api/files` | JSON `{\"path\", \"content\" (base64), \"mode\": \"0644\"}` |\n| `POST` | `api/files` (multipart) | `files={'file': ...}`, `data={'path', 'mode'}` |\n| `GET` | `api/files/{clean_path}` | `stream=True` for download |\n| `GET` | `api/files` | query `path` |\n\n**Header management:**\n- Control plane: `Content-Type: application/json`, `Authorization: Bearer {token}` (if token present)\n- Data plane: `x-agentcube-session-id: {session_id}` (lowercase); Router handles JWT auth\n\n**Base URL resolution for data plane:**\n```\nbase_path = \"/v1/namespaces/{namespace}/code-interpreters/{cr_name}/invocations/\"\nself.base_url = urljoin(router_url, base_path)\n```\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n| Area | Impact |\n|------|--------|\n| **Consumers** | `CodeInterpreterClient` (AR-027) and `AgentRuntimeClient` (AR-028) depend on this layer |\n| **Backward compatibility** | New module; no breaking changes to existing code |\n| **Dependencies** | Adds `requests`, `PyJWT>=2.0.0`, `cryptography` to `pyproject.toml` |\n| **Security** | Auth token read from Kubernetes SA token file (`/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token`); token only sent to control plane, not data plane (Router handles JWT) |\n| **Performance** | Connection pooling via `HTTPAdapter` (default: 10 connections, pool max 10) reduces TLS handshake overhead |\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n| Alternative | Pros | Cons | Decision |\n|-------------|------|------|----------|\n| **`httpx` (async HTTP)** | Async support, modern API, HTTP/2 | SDK currently sync-only; adds complexity for no immediate benefit | Rejected — stick with `requests` for sync simplicity |\n| **Single unified HTTP client** | Simpler surface area | Control plane and data plane have different auth, URL resolution, and header requirements | Rejected — separation of concerns matches server architecture |\n| **Dedicated `Configuration` dataclass** | Centralized config | Current design resolves config at component level; adding a config class would be a breaking refactor | Rejected — follow existing distributed config pattern |\n| **Retry logic in SDK** | Resilience to transient failures | Router and Workload Manager should handle retries; SDK should fail fast to surface issues | Deferred — can add later if needed |\n\n## Upstream Dependencies\n\n- `requests` library (HTTP session, connection pooling)\n- Kubernetes ServiceAccount token file (optional, for control plane auth)\n- Workload Manager service (control plane endpoint)\n- AgentCube Router service (data plane endpoint)\n\n## Status\n\n- [ ] Proposal review\n- [ ] Implementation\n- [ ] Verification\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-029/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-029/proposal.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-029/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775867653387,"end":1775867653400}}}}
